reviews.review_text: Terrapin by Mike Blanks I hope you are all listening and maybe just not commenting. This is legendary. I was there right in front. Most of my 100 shows or so were in front. Mail order worked well. Thank you Matt. To relive this is beyond words and I am so thankful its here. Get out you heads write it up. This and ma y others saved me this year of lockdown. A lifesaver.thanks RIP BRENT AND JERRY. BUT REMEMBER we got to know them for the time they were here. So make it snappy and listen to the archives.!!!
